<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的眼睛睁得很大，他慢慢向后退去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想让我一个人下去？”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要害怕。”马格里布说，“只要你按照我说的做就不会有危险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是一个有魔法的宝物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你回来之后会变得比国王还富有！”魔法师抱着阿拉丁说，“想想吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道，伯父。”阿拉丁担心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个楼梯有五十个台阶，它通向一个有黄金的房间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布说，把男孩抱得更紧了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当你走到最后一步的时候，你会看到四个黄金做的罐子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布的声音像在男孩身上施了咒语一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的担心变成了兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罐子里有宝物吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，孩子。”马格里布说，“小心那些罐子。不要碰它们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“甚至不要让你的裤子的边缘碰到它们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的笑容消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我肯定会远离那些罐子的。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还要小心那些墙。”马格里布说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也不要碰它们。在房间里走的时候要很小心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会非常非常小心的，伯父。”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是别呆太久了。”马格里布笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会尽快的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，你会看到一扇关着的门。”魔法师接着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“命令那扇门打开，就像你命令那块儿石头一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会发现自己在一个美丽的花园里面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是不是保证会带你去另一个花园，阿拉丁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，你保证了，伯父！”阿拉丁开心地说，“在那里我会找到宝物吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是，不是。”魔法师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“注意！顺着花园的路走一百步。那么就离你一生最大的奖赏非常近了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那个宝物？继续说，伯父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个很高的梯子会靠在花园的墙边。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当你向上爬三十步以后，你会看到墙上有一个洞。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在洞里面，你会看到挂在链子上的一个铜灯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿走它，把它放进你的口袋里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爬下来之后把灯拿回来给我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一盏灯？”阿拉丁疑惑地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须把那盏灯拿给我！”马格里布大声说，他的手颤抖着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他冷静了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你回来的时候，可以随意地从花园里的果树上摘水果。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想要的东西都可以拿——只要你有那盏灯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会听你的话，伯父。”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，我的孩子，到时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是一个男人了，不是一个孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你按照我说的做，你很快会变成一个有钱人，最有钱的人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布把阿拉丁带到洞的入口，然后让他往石阶的下面走了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下！”马格里布说着，然后把他的戒指从手指上拿了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个戒指可以保护你远离恐惧和危险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“带着它一直到你回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布往下走，把戒指戴在阿拉丁的手指上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在去吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁走下了石阶，然后回头看着马格里布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他只能看到魔法师头巾下面发亮的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁转身消失在黑暗中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>